secubox-picobrew (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * FastAPI backend with 25+ endpoints
  * Features: Temperature monitoring, fermentation profiles, session logging
  * Sensor support: DS18B20, DHT22, BME280, Tilt, iSpindel, manual
  * Built-in fermentation profiles: Ale Standard, Lager Classic, Belgian Saison
  * Temperature alert system with configurable thresholds
  * Recipe management and brew session tracking
  * CRT-light P31 phosphor theme with amber brewing accents

